node.text:
⁣
Susah banget ya mau produktif dirumah.. Ranjang manggil terus kayaknya?
⁣
GA GA GA, itu gabakal jadi alesan kalian untuk ga produktif dirumah! Karena JC punya tips-tips yang bisa kamu lakuin biar jadi produktif:⁣
⁣
1. Get ready for the day! ⁣
jangan mentang-mentang #dirumahaja jadi pake piyama seharian dongg, yuk ah siap-siap biar semangat jalanin hari! ⁣
⁣
2. Make a schedule⁣
Yuk belajar bikin jadwal! Biar kerjaan dan tugas-tugas kita jadi lebih tertata dan terorganisir⁣
⁣
3. Clean your space⁣
Punya tempat belajar/kerja yang rapih dijamin membangkitkan semangat kalian lagi lohh!⁣
⁣
4. Take a break⁣
Nahh, jangan sampe kalian jadi stress juga yaa karena kebanyakan kerjaan. Pastiin kalian istirahat yang cukup yaa! ⁣
⁣
Yuk sama-sama belajar produktif walaupun dirumah, Semangat!??

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by WORDS_ARE_MAGIC on July 20, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'SHHHHHH IT'S 2AM NOW. I WANNA LET YOU KNOW HOW AM I FEELING. I WAS STANDING INFRONT OF THE MIRROR AND I DON'T UNDERSTAND WHY THE TEARS ALWAYS FALL WITH NO REASON EVERY DAY I TALK TO MYSELF BUT TODAY IS ANOTHER STORY!!! -LET THE CHANGE BEGIN WITH YOU'.

Photo by WORDS_ARE_MAGIC on July 20, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'I SMILE EVEN IF MY HEART SUCKS I TALK TO EVERYONE EVEN IF MY MIND HAS 1000 QUESTIONS. I HIDE MY PAIN EVEN IF I'M NOT FINE. I CRY WHEN NO-ONE SEES ME. I'M DONE PROVING MYSELF TO THIS SOCIETY. YES!! I'M DEPRESSED'.

Photo by WORDS_ARE_MAGIC on July 20, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'YES, I'M DEPRESSED! BUT IT DOESN'T MEAN I QUIT. EVERY DAY IS NEW OPPORTUNITY FOR ME TO BECOME MORE STRONGER NO DEPRESSION IS BIGGER THAN MY AMBITION NOR MY FAMILY'S HAPPINESS NOR MY LIFE. IT IS JUST THE WAY WE THINK OF THINGS CONSTANTLY IN OUR MIND.'.

Photo by WORDS_ARE_MAGIC on July 20, 2020. Image may contain: ‎text that says '‎HEYY!! HAVE TO TELL YOU HOW DID I OVERCOME THIS! STARTED TIME WITH MY FAMILY. STARTED GOING TO MOTIVATION CLASSES(IT'S ?O TO GO DON'T LISTEN NEGATIVE PEOPLE). STARTED DOING YOGA. STARTED MOTIVATING MYSELF THAT NOTHING IS IMPORTANT MORE THAN IN MY LIFE. STARTED DOING WORK WITH NO TIME FREE. I STARTED PLAYING WITH KIDS AND SEEING CARTOONS. ISTARTED TALKING TO ALL MY OLD FRIENDS WHICH MADE ME REMEMBER THOSE BEAUTIFUL OLD DAYS. ISTARTED TO SLEEP MORE. IM HAVING GOOD PROTEIN FOOD.‎'‎.

Photo by WORDS_ARE_MAGIC on July 20, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'AND NOW I CAN SEE NO MORE TEARS ROLLING IN MY EYES WHEN I LOOK INTO THE MIRROR THIS TIME AND VERY MUCH HAPPY NOW WITH ME. DON'T QUIT! TRY TO OVERCOME THE BAD SITUATIONS IN YOUR LIFE! BE STRONG. GENDER DOESN'T MATTER NOW. IT ONLY MATTERS HOW WE TAKE IT TO YOUR MIND. HELP YOURSELF AND YOUR FRIENDS TO GET OUT OF DEPRESSION. GO! THERE IS COLOURFUL LIFE WAITING FOR YOU.'.

node.text:
It was a privilege to be part of the Centenary Meals on Wheels AGM today. These remarkable women, Sue (Past President), Judy (President) and Trisha (Secretary) lead a team of volunteers who provide over 170 meals to locals each week. 

Meals on Wheels provide more than just nutritious food. The delivery of food provides an opportunity to connect, engage and build relationships, helping the most vulnerable in our community. 

During COVID, these volunteers have been working overtime providing this essential service to even more locals. Thank you, thank you, thank you ?.

As part of the AGM, I was honoured to become their patron. I look forward to working closely with this group of dedicated volunteers to support the most vulnerable in our community.

Model of a Granary - Djehutymakht’s tomb contained the most wooden models that have been found to date. Grain was a basic unit of wealth and exchange in Ancient Egypt, and careful accounting of the crop was essential. According to the Bible, Jehovah God targeted the Egyptians and their crops during a few of the Ten Plagues which had devastating effects on the Egyptians.

You can learn more about the Djehutymakht’s tomb on the upcoming virtual Bible tour “Don’t Be Afraid” of the Boston Museum of Fine Arts. Make your reservation today.

node.text:
Axons are classified in two systems. The first one introduced by Erlanger and Gasser, grouped the fibers into three main groups using the letters A, B, and C. These groups, group A, group B, and group C include both the sensory fibers (afferents) and the motor fibres (efferents). 

??The first group A, was subdivided into alpha, beta, gamma, and delta fibers — A?, A?, A?, and A?. The motor neurons of the different motor fibers, were the lower motor neurons – alpha motor neuron, beta motor neuron, and gamma motor neuron having the A?, A?, and A? nerve fibers respectively.

??The Motor Neuron forms synaptic junctions with either extrafusal muscle fibers (skeletal muscle) or intrafusal muscle fibers (thread-like muscle that adjusts tension). Stimulation of these motor neurons induces contraction or shortening of the muscle fibers. 

??Alpha motor neurons induce the contraction of extrafusal muscle fibers upon stimulation, whereas gamma motor neurons induce the contraction of intrafusal muscle fibers upon stimulation. 

??Alpha motor neurons control muscle contraction involved in voluntary movement, whereas gamma motor neurons control muscle contraction in response to external forces acting on the muscle. In response to these external forces, the gamma motor neurons induce the involuntary, reflexive movement called the stretch reflex.

Halitrephes maasi, commonly known on the internet as the firework jellyfish, is a species of deep sea hydrozoan of the family Halicreatidae. The most recent account of the jelly has been found at a depth of 4,000-5,000 feet near the Revillagigedo Archipelago off Baja California Peninsula, Mexico.

Although not much is available regarding this species, research proves that Halitrephes maasi can be found in diverse settings of waters. The hydrozoan has been spotted in both temperate and tropical waters, and has been found in the Atlantic, Indo-Pacific, Antarctic, Mediterrean,and eastern Pacific.
This hydromedusae is typically bathypelagic.
